		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I agree that hacks make this subject more complex. If you can't read Japanese but want to play Japanese RPGs, the only way is to use a hack, and IMO that's a genuine reason to want to make a repro.
<br />
<br />You just can't treat all cases the same, because while trying to avoid the people who are trying to make money out of what's not theirs you also get rid of a lot of honest people.

		

		</td>
